# Runtime data — regenerable locally. The GitHub Actions cron uploads
# data/*.jsonl + status.json to a private Vercel Blob store instead of
# committing them, so no Tippkreis data ever touches this repo. See ADR 0010
# (supersedes the git-commit approach from ADR 0009).
data/
.vercel
